{"tid":2061622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Be water 我希望所有人都識得唱義勇軍進行曲","createTime":"2020-06-12T13:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T16:24:37.000Z","uid":186,"like":34,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1175d29650995b9419fc73e139e77b21474ea2b4","tid":2061622,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"2014年雨傘革命後一直堅持嘅旺角鳩嗚團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ5EmS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ5EmS1.jpg&h=fd512638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個人唱榮光 佢只係一首普通嘅歌<br />\n當二百萬人唱 呢首歌就被賦予意義<br />\n國家都要害怕呢首榮光 <br />\n<br />\n義勇軍進行曲<br />\n一個人唱係玩膠<br />\n當二百萬人唱 呢首義士勇武進行曲<br />\n<br />\n就好似Be water<br />\nNow you put water into a cup, it becomes the cup,<br />\n you put water into a bottle, it becomes the bottle,<br />\n you put it in a teapot, it becomes the teapot.<br />\n<br />\n佢就會被賦予另一意義<br />\n國歌法立咗 不用改詞 不改音 <br />\n我相信香港會令中共<br />\n最終會害怕呢首歌<br />\nIdea is bulletproof"},{"pid":"6c0d5a3ceef7cbeb01ebc2a255900ac59312685c","tid":2061622,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔學唱國歌《義勇軍進行曲》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起來！不願做奴隸的人們！（起身啦！唔想做港奴的人們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！（我地要不惜血肉，要建立<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新嘅</span></strong></span>長城）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，（中華民族依家到咗最危險嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。（咁慘烈 去到最後 迫住叫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n起來！起來！起來！（起身啦 出嚟啦 返來啦）<br />\n<br />\n我們萬眾一心，（我哋萬眾一心，一個共同目標，唯一出路）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（敵人有炮火都要前進啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（TG 警嫂 繼續向前進）<br />\n<br />\n前進！前進！進！（一定要向前進，唔好退，唔好走，唔好做返港豬，唔好移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"7358e25bb2daaf50f59036efbbc588075b5b5b91","tid":2061622,"uid":68132,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"黨媒：國安法喚醒香港人愛國心"},{"pid":"f580d5fd785ba5cc6ca8254a5d886d8fc2f7e864","tid":2061622,"uid":61282,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"啲差佬同法官識讀心㗎，你照原版唱佢都睇得出你背後企圖係搞港獨"},{"pid":"4bb6e59384ed3c2cc3b328a9370d8b3f6c5e3c95","tid":2061622,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7358e25bb2daaf50f59036efbbc588075b5b5b91","tid":2061622,"uid":68132,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"黨媒：國安法喚醒香港人愛國心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"Pepe 都被香港賦予新意義<br />\n外國人 原作者都學習pepe 係香港嘅新意義"},{"pid":"03edcdd7bc347dd2e7fa6b369676d069fbb60942","tid":2061622,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f580d5fd785ba5cc6ca8254a5d886d8fc2f7e864","tid":2061622,"uid":61282,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"啲差佬同法官識讀心㗎，你照原版唱佢都睇得出你背後企圖係搞港獨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"正正就係話俾中共同世界聽<br />\nIdea is bulletproof <br />\n不改一字 呢首會成為我哋嘅歌"},{"pid":"7be85f04d0cba3a449893756d51df64148aa3874","tid":2061622,"uid":48357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f580d5fd785ba5cc6ca8254a5d886d8fc